					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="This Is the Science Behind Thriving Workplace Cultures" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/20150723161017-inspire-team-cant-afford-fancy-perks-teamwork-meeting-office-coworkers.jpeg" rel="share" />

					
							
								
				
				
